---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="border-t border-[var(--color-line)] mt-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-14">
    <div class="rounded-2xl bg-[var(--color-ink)] text-[var(--color-paper)] p-8 sm:p-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">
        Your website should be winning you customers.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[var(--color-paper-deep)] opacity-80 max-w-md">
        Fiorverso builds fast, conversion-focused websites for Baltimore small businesses.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://fiorverso.com"
        class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] px-6 py-3 font-medium hover:bg-[var(--color-accent-deep)] transition-colors"
      >Start a project →</a>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-10 text-sm text-[var(--color-ink-faint)]">
      © {year} Fiorverso · FYG Web Services LLC · Baltimore, MD
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
